{"title": "Sony is releasing a limited edition gold PS4 for $249", "content": " \nThe slimmed-down PlayStation 4 is getting a new gold edition. Today Sony announced a limited edition version of the console, with 1TB of storage and a gold color scheme, that will be available for $249 \u2014 $50 cheaper than the normal model. The catch is that the console will only be available for a limited time. You can snag one between June 9th and 17th. Sony also says that there will be \u201cadditional discounts on software and accessories\u201d during that period, though no specifics have been announced just yet.\n"}
